snippet.title: VIGILANCER 2099 - Official UE5 Cyberpunk Gameplay Teaser #2
snippet.description:
Vigilancer 2099 is a cyberpunk bounty hunting game inspired by prey 2 and blade runner. What you are seeing is prototype gameplay now using the latest Unreal Engine 5 with a lot more to come!
Wishlist on Steam!: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1737960/Vigilance_2099/
Website is now Live: https://www.vigilance2099.com/
For more info, check out our twitter page: https://twitter.com/NasNakarus
Feel free to join our discord! : https://discord.gg/CxUPhzC
